<paragraph blockId="51.[151,1436,1037,1444]" pageId="51" pageNumber="52">
<materialsCitation collectionCode="MNHN" pageId="51" pageNumber="52" specimenCount="2" typeStatus="holotype">
Note. Séguy did not explicitly state that he based his species on 
<specimenCount box="[888,1035,1101,1124]" pageId="51" pageNumber="52" type="generic">one specimen</specimenCount>
only, nor did he use the word “ 
<typeStatus pageId="51" pageNumber="52">Holotype</typeStatus>
” or “Type” or similar expression in the published text, but only 
<specimenCount box="[946,1094,1133,1156]" pageId="51" pageNumber="52" type="generic">one specimen</specimenCount>
is present in 
<collectionCode box="[1241,1322,1133,1156]" country="France" httpUri="http://biocol.org/urn:lsid:biocol.org:col:34988" lsid="urn:lsid:biocol.org:col:34988" name="Museum National d'Histoire Naturelle" pageId="51" pageNumber="52">MNHN</collectionCode>
