), the distal corners are somewhat bent dorsally so they appear slightly too short in the figure.
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="51.[151,1436,1491,1943]" pageId="51" pageNumber="52">Cerci strongly curved in lateral view. Surstylus narrow, blunt distally, bare below. Process of the bacilliform sclerite strongly pointed.</paragraph>
